# TypeScript Standards

Read and follow the "TypeScript Standards" section in `CONTRIBUTING.md`.

Key rules: ESM with `.js` extensions, `import type` for type-only imports, kebab-case files, `logger` from `@alerthq/core` (no `console.*`), `withRetry` for all I/O, `"default"` key in package.json exports.
